eschr

i love m.c. escher. so when learning c++ and opengl i created this program to have an interesting challenge. 

http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

have fun!


keys:
q/a	flatness
z	reset flatness
w/s	eschr position
x	reset eschr position
e/d	colors

i/k, j/l, u/o rotate eschr
m	reset eschr rotation

cursor left/right rotate surface

esc	quit

